Look at Luclin. Wizard spires? Druid circles? What are those? Park your ass under the spires (One on each continent) and wait 15 minutes if you want to go up there. Is your raid already underway? Well too bad, because CoH doesn't work in this zone, I hope your friends can clear back to you! Want to kill the Emperor? Lord Seru? The Creator? Have fun spending months getting keys or camping your guildmates rare drop components from rare mobs to form crappy weaponry that ends up doing jack for damage anyway. FoH didn't even have the manpower to take Seru down, they had to bring in nukers from other guilds because the melees may as well have been beating on him with Twizzlers.<br>
